title: New Creator: "Dekkster"
body:
Name: Dekkster

Socials: 
https://twitter.com/DekksterGaming
https://www.youtube.com/c/dekkstergaming
https://www.twitch.tv/dekkster
https://discord.gg/nDccp58E

Info: Dekkster is a premier Hearthstone streamer that averages around 500 viewers per stream and also posts Hearthstone YouTube videos that attracts thousands of views. With over 100,000 followers across his socials, Dekkster is a Hearthstone fan favorite.

Targeted Use Case: Coaching, allowing fans to play in stream, YouTube gated content, exclusive Discord access. 

Community Treasury Grant Tier: $500

A "Yes" vote would approve Dekkster as a creator, and provide a $500 grant.

A "No" vote would reject Dekkster from the platform.
author: 0xa1e4270381e381E75ef6e4dDa1a27337a4Be0939
